Package crazyballrun.game.utilities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GraphGenerator
    The GraphGenerator generates a graph with neighborhood relations between QuadTree-leaf-nodes.
    PathFinder
    The PathFinder calculates the shortest path between two nodes in a graph.
    PathFinder.Node
    Representation of one node of the graph.
    Position3D
    The Position3D class represents a pseudo-3d position with 2d-coordinates and the layer.
    QuadTree<Value extends java.lang.Comparable & java.io.Serializable>
    The QuadTree class is a descrete representation of a continous domain.
    Rectangle3D
    Rectangle3D defines a rectangle on a particular layer (not over several layers!)
    Vector2D
    The Vector2D class is a utility for translation and rotation of position coordinates.
